{
  "texts": [
    "It continuously senses the network status and autonomously detects faults.",
    "This capability allows the network to quickly identify and resolve issues, ensuring high availability and reliability.",
    "By leveraging real-time data collection and advanced analytics, the NDT enhances the self-healing abilities of a network and improves its overall stability and performance.",
    "The NDT performs real-time data sensing from the physical network and synchronizes its state.",
    "Detection models are used to detect anomalies in network behavior using historical data and realtime inputs."
  ]
}